{"tid":1557530,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"政治問題就要由政治解決，釋放所有被捕抗爭者、撤銷其控罪","createTime":"2019-09-10T07:00:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T07:01:13.000Z","uid":319948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b4954435223545b5616b0379144023e78271b4fe","tid":1557530,"uid":319948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:00:11.000Z","msg":"根本政治問題就要由政治解決 面對著咁多人俾人charge 仲要係唔同類型 照咁樣落去司法制度可一定會癱瘓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解五大訴求之一 係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">釋放所有被捕抗爭者、撤銷其控罪</span></strong> 就係因由政治問題所產生出嚟既所謂犯罪根本就應該由政治解決 而唔係單單靠班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去拉人解決 我俾你拉夠100 1000 你咪慢慢審個十年八載都分分鐘未撚解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最尾你可以只係對成個運動既帶頭者進行控罪 但你拉咁多人只會令個問題繼續惡化  但問題係我地根本就無大台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  政府你咪繼續放縱你班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下邊個笑到最後<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"bd8b08b1b56ee70c9d79431dad773d5c73800c72","tid":1557530,"uid":319948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kaaARJn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkaaARJn.jpg&h=d23388ea&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}